exceptions.exn: In environment this : nid A : Type pr : protocol I : dstatelet -> pred nid -> Prop ii : InductiveInv pr I s1, s2 : state sc : schedule t, t' : proc this (mkWorld pr) A Hcoh : s1 \\In Coh (mkWorld (ProtocolWithIndInv ii)) Hstep : Coh (mkWorld pr) s1 /\\ Coh (mkWorld pr) s2 Unable to unify "Coh (mkWorld pr) s2" with "s2 \\In Coh (mkWorld (ProtocolWithIndInv ii))".

original: intros Hcoh Hstep. apply pstep_network_sem in Hstep. eapply step_coh in Hstep. apply (proj2 Hstep).
